posting_body: ['Welcome to Prism', 'A Prism of Possibility.', 'The Mid-Market neighborhood is a treasure trove of hidden gems — social, cultural and culinary.', 'It’s a vibrant spectrum of restaurants, cafés, theater, nightlife, shops, museums, plazas and parklets.', 'This is the new Mid-Market… a renaissance in action.', 'The official Walk Score rates Mid-Market a “walking, transit and biking paradise.”', 'Many of San Francisco’s largest employers are within a 15-minute walk or 8-minute bike ride.', 'By foot, bike, train, bus, subway, cable car.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Free WiFi in Common Areas', 'Pet Friendly Community', 'Working Nooks throughout Building', 'Grill and Kitchen', 'Fitness Center with Peloton Bikes', 'Lounge Seating', 'Resident Storage Lockers', 'Dog Park', 'Parcel Lockers with Cold Storage', 'City Views / Bay Views', 'Living Room / Co-Working Lounge', 'Picnic Lawn', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
